  <h1>aka.dog</h1>
  <p>
    A small reference index of where Microsoft's cloud services actually live - the
    <code>*.cloud.microsoft</code> endpoints, their old hosts, and what moved where. Entries are the
    source of truth; every page is a derived view.
  </p>
  <p>
    Start at the <a href="/index">full index</a>, or jump to
    <a href="/index/microsoft/cloud-microsoft">cloud.microsoft endpoints</a>,
    <a href="/index/microsoft/end-user">end-user surfaces</a>, or the
    <a href="/index/deprecated">deprecated</a> list. Append <code>.json</code> to any of these for the
    machine-readable view.
  </p>
</Layout>
